│  ## Database Schema Summary                                                  │
│                                                                              │
│  The implementation includes the following tables:                           │
│                                                                              │
│  1. **users** - User accounts with authentication and profile information    │
│  2. **favorites** - User favorite comics (many-to-many relationship)         │
│  3. **reading_history** - Track user reading progress                        │
│  4. **comics** - Comic metadata including title, author, status, genres,     │
│  ratings                                                                     │
│  5. **ratings** - User ratings for comics (1-5 scale)                        │
│  6. **comments** - User comments on comics (supports nested replies via      │
│  parent_id)                                                                  │
│  7. **chapters** - Comic chapters with ordering and publication status       │
│  8. **pages** - Individual pages within chapters                             │
│                                                                              │
│  All models have proper relationships defined with SQLAlchemy, including     │
│  cascading deletes where appropriate. The database has been successfully     │
│  created and verified.                                                       │
│                                                                              │
